%h1 About

%h3 HNSearch

%p HNSearch provides real-time full-text search for the <a href="http://news.ycombinator.com">HackerNews</a> community site. Source code is available on <a href="https://github.com/algolia/hn-search">GitHub</a>. Search backend is implemented using <a href="http://www.algolia.com">Algolia</a> instant search engine.

%h3 How it works

%p Every 2 minutes, last 1000 HN items (stories, comments, polls) are sent to Algolia's indexing API. Items from the the last 48 hours are refreshed every hour.
%p Data are indexed on 3 different servers for high availability, hosted in St-Louis/USA.

